Datatype is always string
 {{&lt; get-parameters-test-01 &ldquo;foo&rdquo; &gt;}}
=&gt; []string{&#34;foo&#34;}  {{&lt; get-parameters-test-01 &ldquo;foo\nbar&rdquo; &gt;}}
=&gt; []string{&#34;foo\\nbar&#34;} &ldquo;\&rdquo; gets quoted with &ldquo;\&rdquo; {{&lt; get-parameters-test-01 false &gt;}}
=&gt; []string{&#34;false&#34;} boolean values is true (non emtpy) {{&lt; get-parameters-test-01 1 &gt;}}
=&gt; []string{&#34;1&#34;}  {{&lt; get-parameters-test-01 &ldquo;0.5&rdquo; &gt;}}
=&gt; []string{&#34;0.5&#34;}  {{&lt; get-parameters-test-01 &ldquo;&rdquo; &gt;}}
=&gt; []string{&#34;&#34;}  {{&lt; get-parameters-test-01 1e3 &gt;}}
=&gt; []string{&#34;1e3&#34;} not 1000   A) {{&lt; get-parameters-test-01 &lsquo;foo&rsquo; &gt;}}

