Positional parameters  {{&lt; get-parameters-test-02 1 2 3 &gt;}}
=&gt; []string{&#34;1&#34;, &#34;2&#34;, &#34;3&#34;}  {{&lt; get-parameters-test-02 1 foo 3 &gt;}}
=&gt; []string{&#34;1&#34;, &#34;foo&#34;, &#34;3&#34;}  {{&lt; get-parameters-test-02 1 foo bar 3 &gt;}}
=&gt; []string{&#34;1&#34;, &#34;foo&#34;, &#34;bar&#34;, &#34;3&#34;}  {{&lt; get-parameters-test-02 1 &ldquo;foo bar&rdquo; 3 &gt;}}
=&gt; []string{&#34;1&#34;, &#34;foo bar&#34;, &#34;3&#34;}   Named parameters https://discourse.gohugo.io/t/shortcodes-best-practice-for-named-parameters-quoting/10253
{{always quote the values using &quot;}}
 {{&lt; get-parameters-test-02 arg1=&ldquo;1&rdquo; arg2=&ldquo;2&rdquo; arg3=&ldquo;3&rdquo; &gt;}}

